Quickstrike:





Quickstrike looked at Dark Mouse. "Well, let's go. Th' faster we 
get out there, th' faster we can enjoy th' outdoors." He looked 
back at Black Arachnia. "See ya when we get back, sugar-bot." He 
winked at her. He lead the way down to the ramp.
